    "description": "CORR是一款困难的灵魂 Boss Rush 动作角色扮演游戏，您将通过奔跑和射击、劈砍的方式挑战各种强大的 Boss。为了经受得住CORR的奇异、黑暗和离奇的世界，提升并定制您的战士建筑，使用狂暴的力量、药剂、护身符等。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330260/extras/2cd4b129441ca92a4e485f279914c6f2.poster.avif?t=1761137930\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330260/extras/2cd4b129441ca92a4e485f279914c6f2.webm?t=1761137930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330260/extras/2cd4b129441ca92a4e485f279914c6f2.mp4?t=1761137930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]无敌冲刺。[]体力/能量管理。[]触感强烈的近战和射击战斗。</ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330260/extras/94bdd4267945a8851192900b84717a24.avif?t=1761137930\" width=705 height=627 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330260/extras/88a4f64d7b1a317f711c9e5b16cf4c62.avif?t=1761137930\" width=581 height=326 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boss战斗：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]做好准备迎接CORR的庞大 Boss 队伍，挑战多阶段的 Boss 战。[]非线性进展。卡在一个 Boss 战中？试试其他的一段时间。[]厌倦了不能重玩你喜欢的 Boss 战吗？在CORR中，所有 Boss 战都可以通过记忆碎片重玩。</ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330260/extras/822d96949a43883d8e4824fb16380327.avif?t=1761137930\" width=581 height=326 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色发展：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]获得护身符，用被动技能定制您的角色建筑。[]获得可以在战斗中激活的独特狂暴力量。[]收集材料并酿造自己的消耗品。[]获得可以以独特方式增加游戏难度的咒语，以挑战自己并获得独特奖励。<li>提升您的角色属性。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330260/extras/84f73ce4ccc51ae4077528f88e4f71d7.avif?t=1761137930\" width=581 height=500 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]通过解释物品描述、神秘的角色对话、环境叙事等，拼凑出停滞世界的事件。[]包括分支的NPC任务线。</ul>",
